{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"最新指示传到革委会","authors":["学江"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":10,"day":9}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新指示传到革委会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜讯乘着东风吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过千山和万水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席最新指示发表了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消息传到革委会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老主任，军代表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜在心头笑在眉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喇叭筒、铁锤手中拿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一前一后步如飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边走，一边谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动得双眼滚热泪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席指出光明路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是咱“重新学习的极好机会”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个说，最新指示是战鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战鼓冬冬显神威；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把修正主义连根铲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把官气暮气抛入垃圾堆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个说，最新指示是春雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨滋润禾苗肥；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新老干部发扬革命好传统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命斗志坚不可摧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个说，最新指示是号角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们工人阶级要步步紧跟随；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流几身汗水，滚一身油泥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持劳动最可贵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个说，最新指示是灯塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五湖四海放光辉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮万里长征路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘胜前进头不回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边走边谈到车间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间象一锅沸腾的水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大红的标语墙上挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八镑的大锤手中挥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部群众同洒汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也赶来我也追，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厂里一片新气象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命生产展翅飞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"指示"}]}]}